description: The wormiest collectables on the Tezos Blockchain and throughout the galaxy! 3,333 wormy friends waiting to be collected through their wormholes. 3 waves of 1,111 each with new sets of randomized parts! Flat pricing curve of 3 Tez. After all Wormyholes are sold, 10% will be donated to a charity voted on by the wormy community.
